{"tid":560320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新田購物城門可羅雀　黃定光：任何商場都要守一段時間","createTime":"2018-02-14T03:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T04:17:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"de3a6215f22b6620793f49f413f046922e8b6099","tid":560320,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180214/s00001/b5bc7ce6c5c9f6490131410709ca0fd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180214%2Fs00001%2Fb5bc7ce6c5c9f6490131410709ca0fd3.jpg&h=f451a528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新田購物城2月3日起試業，但場面冷清，只有一成店舖開業，遊客人流稀疏。有份籌辦購物城的立法會議員黃定光在港台節目指，絕大數接觸的業界和朋友都認為購物城方向正確，只是任何商場都要「守」一段時間：「希望新田唔洗守咁耐啦，依樣嘢我有信心嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n黃定光指出，目前有商戶不足及人流稀疏兩大問題，他指全場214間舖，89間已簽約，當中只有20間舖戶在2月3日試業時開業，給人形象十室九空，減卻市民遊玩意欲，形成惡性循環，故目前先敦促商戶開檔，他建議商戶先不要太執着裝潢，例如未必要裝冷氣、招牌可以簡易點，先開業「谷旺個場」。黃定光又指，為吸引更多商戶駐場，故此購物城已決定到7月1日才收租。<br />\n<br />\n黃定光表示，已與香港及內地的旅行團洽談，討論能否加設新田購物城作景點，另外多作宣傳推廣，期望購物城更加興旺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180214/s00001/1518575919695\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180214%2Fs00001%2F1518575919695&d=S0JqnjFrO9tkynOqOojc%2B26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=99bcc84f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180214%2Fs00001%2F1518575919695&h=a8ec3181\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180214/s00001/1518575919695</a>"},{"pid":"6557ef3b8d15abe461efc5f5e3314307e591dba9","tid":560320,"uid":9230,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:47:56.000Z","msg":"其實.......原來佢開會瞓著咗，對個社會更有貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2137b94ae220b00d5e962621bb109a952acebe20","tid":560320,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢伯"},{"pid":"8af87bb9c0297daf372b04319b4b876023a56568","tid":560320,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"即係有125間租唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c830f041e1030be6a49ef5fd68808bf615dca61","tid":560320,"uid":164751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:00:28.000Z","msg":"叫佢去守囉, 守埋夜囉"},{"pid":"ea5bd57851c842dd0e2adf5b56867de2024f8066","tid":560320,"uid":164751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:03:01.000Z","msg":"叫佢谷精谷旺個場"},{"pid":"3d9412675a01d345546a13c02c205884a005718c","tid":560320,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:04:55.000Z","msg":"大老闆, 包租公叫人守?<br />\n點解佢又放租比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成件事好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8810045cdac7532fd91c4c12ec0ff852d43e3fdb","tid":560320,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:07:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他建議商戶先不要太執着裝潢，例如未必要裝冷氣、招牌可以簡易點，先開業「谷旺個場」</span><br />\n室外地方唔裝,D客會入黎?"},{"pid":"440b51e03a0f4026b44f3f3ca099a8562046f3be","tid":560320,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6557ef3b8d15abe461efc5f5e3314307e591dba9","tid":560320,"uid":9230,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:47:56.000Z","msg":"其實.......原來佢開會瞓著咗，對個社會更有貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:17:36.000Z","msg":"呢d真係廢老"}]}